      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Quantities of interest (construct stiffness, peak load at 1% permanent deformation) directly correspond to ASTM F1717 acceptance criteria and are mechanistically linked to clinical performance indicators identified in predicate device submissions."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
