      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities conducted on geometrically and materially identical constructs to those described in the 510(k) submission. Test configuration per ASTM F1717 is the regulatory standard benchmark for this device class."
    }
